OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with rain spreading across
OL,7,Ffrom the west. Rain will continue
OL,8,Fthrough the rest of the night, with
OL,9,Foccasional heavy bursts in the early
OL,10,Fhours.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FEarly rain across northern
OL,13,Fareas will quickly clear. Then bright
OL,14,Fspells and frequent showers for the
OL,15,Frest of the day, some likely heavy and
OL,16,Fthundery in the afternoon.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,19,FVariable amounts of cloud with showers
OL,20,For a few longer spells of rain. Often
OL,21,Frather warm in any sunny spells.
